      {
         "id": "SECTION_game_time",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "### Why play?\n\nThe number systems and tools we have studied so far are based on the human body—a fact that has held true for thousands of years, as shown by bones found in various locations (<htcite0>; <htcite1>; <htcite2>) and represented in **Figure 1**.\n\n",
               "source": [
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "a4f22e25-5839-407f-a1aa-634521d52b42",
                     "text": "González Redondo, Francisco A., et al.,",
                     "page": "pp. 174 - 177, 180 - 182",
                     "date_time": {
                        "type": "gregory",
                        "year": "2024",
                        "month": "06",
                        "day": "12"
                     }
                  },
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "ceffba8a-43be-4de3-a5c8-27cdf81311b1",
                     "text": "Puente, Francisco Barriga,",
                     "page": "pp. 21 - 23",
                     "date_time": {
                        "type": "gregory",
                        "year": "2024",
                        "month": "07",
                        "day": "25"
                     }
                  },
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "cd61bc64-1358-4bfd-b343-3629facaa3b4",
                     "text": "González Redondo, Francisco A.",
                     "page": "",
                     "date_time": {
                        "type": "gregory",
                        "year": "2024",
                        "month": "10",
                        "day": "27"
                     }
                  }
               ],
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "markdown",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"desc\"><img id=\"img9\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('img9', '0%')\" src=\"\" class=\"imgcenter\"/><b>Figure 1</b>: Representation of a baboon bone with markings. This image was created by Enrique Silván Pobes and appears in the work of Francisco A. González Redondo et al.. The original is available on ResearchNet (<htcite0>) and is shown here with permission from Dr. Francisco A. González Redondo for republication.</p>",
               "source": [
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "adaed4fb-9c50-4ef9-ab79-c65f3c0629b8",
                     "text": "González Redondo, Francisco A., et al.",
                     "page": "",
                     "date_time": {
                        "type": "gregory",
                        "year": "2024",
                        "month": "02",
                        "day": "01"
                     }
                  }
               ],
               "date_time": [
                  {
                     "type": "gregory",
                     "year": "2010",
                     "month": "-1",
                     "day": "-1"
                  }
               ],
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "However, simply reading a text may often not be enough to understand its content. Teachers and students involved in a study demonstrated the validity of homework or house tasks as a way to reinforce knowledge (<htcite0>).\n\nGiven this scenario, we at *History Tracers* bring games like this one, which help people reinforce the knowledge acquired through texts.",
               "source": [
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "0e18261e-e542-4bd1-a074-a42b9c0eb25d",
                     "text": "Costa, M., Cardoso, A. P., Lacerda, C., Lopes, A., & Gomes, C.",
                     "page": "",
                     "date_time": {
                        "type": "gregory",
                        "year": "2016",
                        "month": "",
                        "day": ""
                     }
                  }
               ],
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "markdown",
               "PostMention": ""
            }
         ]
      },
      {
         "id": "SECTION_game",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "<p><h3>Discovering America (<i>Abya Ayala</i>)</h3><b>Objective and rules:</b>Our objective is to translate the indigenous numerations that will appear, either on <i>Yupana</i> format or in the Mesoamerican format. With each value you translate, you will learn about an indigenous region in America (<i>Abya Ayala</i>). You can advance to the next mission by clicking on <i class=\"fa-solid fa-play\" style=\"color: Tomato;\"></i>. At the end, you will receive a medal (<i class=\"fa-solid fa-medal\" style=\"color:gold;\"></i>) for your work.</p><p><b>Note:</b> To read a number on the Yupana, we must look at all four squares. In contrast, Mesoamerican numbers are represented in a single square.</p><p><table id=\"yupana1\" class=\"tawapukllay\"><tr><th colspan=\"4\">Translate the first line and discover indigenous constructions.</th></tr> <tr id=\"tf3\"><td colspan=\"3\" id=\"tc1f3\"><span id=\"gameImage\"></span></td><td id=\"tc4f3\"><div id=\"descImage\"></div> <span style=\"font-size: 3em; color: Tomato;\"><i id=\"nextLevel\" class=\"fa-solid fa-play\"></i></span></td></tr> <tr id=\"tf1\"><td id=\"tc1f1\">&nbsp;</td> <td id=\"tc2f1\">&nbsp;</td> <td id=\"tc3f1\">&nbsp;</td> <td id=\"tc4f1\">&nbsp;</td></tr> <tr id=\"tf2\"><td id=\"tc1f2\">&nbsp;</div></td> <td id=\"tc2f2\">&nbsp;</td> <td id=\"tc3f2\">&nbsp;</td> <td id=\"tc4f2\">&nbsp;</td></tr> </table>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"desc\">We work with <i>Yupana</i> using the <i>\"Yupana Inka Tawa Pukllay\"</i> method, developed and published by Dhavit Prem (<htcite0>) of the Yupanki Association (<htcite1>).<br />The use of Mesoamerican numbers is based on the work of Orlando Josué Casares Contreras, José M. Gamboa Cetina y Venus Sarahí Estrella Cabrera (<htcite2> ; <htcite3>). Additionally, we incorporate the work of Francisco Barriga Puente, and Ximena Catepillán (<htcite4> ; <htcite5>).<br /> Finally, we utilize various counting methods inspired by the work of Francisco A. González Redondo <i>et al.</i> (<htcite6>).</p>",
               "source": [
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "2d2ea4a5-506b-4dbf-aaa4-3a10a8fbbd9c",
                     "text": "Prem, Dhavit",
                     "page": "",
                     "date_time": {
                        "type": "gregory",
                        "year": "2024",
                        "month": "07",
                        "day": "25"
                     }
                  },
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "a62b520a-f443-4d83-ab51-b99c9a46dab8",
                     "text": "Prem, Dhavit",
                     "page": "",
                     "date_time": {
                        "type": "gregory",
                        "year": "2024",
                        "month": "04",
                        "day": "01"
                     }
                  },
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "ad11b3b2-8cdf-4d71-9cb7-2ac241850945",
                     "text": "Casares Contreras, Orlando & Cetina, José & Cabrera, Venus Sarahí",
                     "page": "ResearchGate",
                     "date_time": {
                        "type": "gregory",
                        "year": "2024",
                        "month": "07",
                        "day": "25"
                     }
                  },
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "eca99877-c520-4569-a71c-0a5b3dd77dc4",
                     "text": "Casares Contreras, Orlando & Cetina, José & Cabrera, Venus Sarahí",
                     "page": "Revista",
                     "date_time": {
                        "type": "gregory",
                        "year": "2024",
                        "month": "07",
                        "day": "25"
                     }
                  },
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "ceffba8a-43be-4de3-a5c8-27cdf81311b1",
                     "text": "Puente, Francisco Barriga",
                     "page": "",
                     "date_time": {
                        "type": "gregory",
                        "year": "2024",
                        "month": "07",
                        "day": "25"
                     }
                  },
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "ced67eaf-7378-4589-9166-07f799969e3e",
                     "text": "Catepillán, Ximena",
                     "page": "",
                     "date_time": {
                        "type": "gregory",
                        "year": "2024",
                        "month": "04",
                        "day": "26"
                     }
                  },
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "a4f22e25-5839-407f-a1aa-634521d52b42",
                     "text": "González Redondo, Francisco A., et al.",
                     "page": "",
                     "date_time": {
